---
title: Sweet Potato 'Steaks' with Smoky Black Beans, Tomato Salad and Quinoa
description: Sweet potato toasts are all the rage, and we wanted to try is out for ourselves! We've turned our own sweet potatoes into 'steaks' and topped them with a smoky, salty black bean medley for a fun variation of beans on toast!
